s-traveler-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDelta%20One%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20airline's%20business-class%20seat%20on%20long-haul%20flights%2C%20offering%20lie-flat%20seats%20and%20a%20host%20of%20other%20amenities.%20I've%20flown%20Delta%20One%20once%20before%2C%20from%20New%20York%20to%20San%20Francisco%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-expenses-used-credit-card-points-honeymoon-hotels-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20honeymoon%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eso%20I%20was%20thrilled%20to%20see%20what%20it%20was%20like%20to%20fly%20Delta%20One%20internationally.%20My%20Delta%20One%20ticket%20for%20the%20flight%20from%20Brussels%20to%20Atlanta%20cost%20%241%2C356.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20luxury%20ticket%20was%20amazing%2C%20but%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20a%20few%20aspects%20of%20the%20Delta%20One%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20bag%20checking%20and%20security%20experiences%20weren't%20exceptional.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20boarding%20area%20of%20a%20Delta%20airline.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b7551f194a2d49b8af9595%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Pettyjohn%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20flew%20Delta%20One%20out%20of%20JFK%20in%20February%2C%20I%20was%20ushered%20into%20a%20closed-off%20area%20of%20the%20airport%20for%20check-in.%20Attentive%20Delta%20agents%20checked%20my%20bags%20for%20me%2C%20offered%20me%20water%20while%20I%20waited%2C%20and%20escorted%20me%20through%20a%20private%20security%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20check-in%20process%20differs%20based%20on%20the%20airport%20or%20country%20you're%20flying%20out%20of%2C%20and%20because%20I%20was%20flying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomparing-every-upgrade-delta-flights-cabins-economy-premium-2025-4%5C%22%20t