Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-one-virgin-atlantic-airport-lounges-lax-which-is-better-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDelta%20One%20lounge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20by%20far%20the%20most%20luxurious%20airport%20lounge%20I've%20ever%20been%20inside.%20However%2C%20Delta%20One%20lounges%20are%20only%20available%20at%20a%20few%20airports%20in%20the%20US%2C%20so%20when%20you're%20traveling%20internationally%2C%20a%20business%20class%20ticket%20will%20get%20you%20access%20to%20partner%20lounges%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20terminal%20at%20the%20Brussels%20airport%20featured%20The%20View%20lounge%2C%20an%20airy%20space%20with%20a%20plethora%20of%20cushy%20chairs%2C%20a%20huge%20breakfast%20buffet%2C%20a%20quiet%20library%2C%20and%20a%20bar%20with%20self-serve%20soft%20drinks%20and%20alcohol.%20If%20your%20ticket%20doesn't%20give%20you%20automatic%20entry%2C%20you%20can%20also%20purchase%20a%20day%20pass%20to%20The%20View%20for%20around%20%2455.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20pampered%20in%20the%20lounge%2C%20where%20I%20grabbed%20a%20latte%20from%20one%20of%20several%20coffee%20machines%20and%20enjoyed%20a%20filling%20breakfast.%20There%20was%20even%20a%20chef%20making%20custom%20omelets%20for%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELounge%20access%20was%20a%20huge%20perk%20of%20my%20Delta%20One%20ticket%2C%20especially%20because%20my%20flight%20ended%20up%20being%20delayed%20over%20an%20hour.%20It%20was%20much%20more%20relaxing%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20quiet%20lounge%20than%20to%20try%20to%20find%20somewhere%20to%20sit%20at%20my%20gate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20seat%20had%20some%20surprises.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20business%20class%20seat%20on%20an%20international%20Delta%20plane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b7563b194a2d49b8af95c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Pettyjohn%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20finally%20time%20to%20board%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-back-of-plane-is-favorite-seat-long-haul-flights-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20plane%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20couldn't%20wait%20to%20see%20my%20seat.%20I%20knew%20it%20would%20have%20a%20pillow%20and%20lie-down%20capabilities%2C%20but%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20see%20what%20other%20amenities%20it%20offered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20disappointed.%20In%20addition%20to%20allowing%20me%20to%20lie%20down%2C%20the%20seat%20had%20a%20massage%20function%20to%20offer%20extra%20comfort.%20It%20also%20featured%20a%20cubby%20for%20my%20shoes%2C%20which%20I%20took%20advantage%20of%20immediately%20so%20I%20could%20wear%20the%20slippers%20Delta%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20loved%20the%20headphones%20and%20care%20kit%20the%20airline%20provided.%20The%20kit%20included%20an%20eye%20mask%2C%20earplugs%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-are-making-compression-socks-cool-aging-inflammation-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esocks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20toiletries%20like%20a%20toothbrush%20and%20hand%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20seat%20also%20came%20with%20a%20mattress%20pad.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20of%20a%20Delta%20One%20seat%20on%20an%20international%20flight%20and%20the%20same%20seat%20with%20a%20mattress%20pad%20on%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b75759194a2d49b8af95d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Pettyjohn%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20biggest%20benefit%20of%20flying%20Delta%20One%20is%20that%20the%20seat%20lies%20flat%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20sleep%20on%20a%20long%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reclining%20seat%20would%20have%20been%20plenty%20for%20me%2C%20but%20I%20was%20delighted%20to%20discover%20that%20Delta%20also%20provides%20a%20mattress%20pad%20for%20customers%20flying%20Delta%20One.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20first%20sit%20down%2C%20the%20pad%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20lumbar%20pillow%2C%20but%20you%20can%20unroll%20it%20to%20create%20a%20mattress%20pad%20for%20extra%20comfort.%20I%20used%20the%20pad%20for%20nearly%20half%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-seats-on-plane-which-to-avoid-frequent-flyer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20loving%20the%20additional%20layer%20when%20I%20was%20watching%20a%20movie%20or%20trying%20to%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20curtain%20dividing%20business%20class%20from%20premium%20select%20was%20never%20closed.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20woman%20on%20a%20Delta%20plane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b763afa17a8c5b4053e43f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Pettyjohn%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I've%20flown%20economy%20or%20in%20the%20main%20cabin%20in%20the%20past%2C%20I%20often%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20see%20the%20first%20few%20rows%20of%20the%20plane%2C%20as%20flight%20attendants%20typically%20close%20the%20curtain%20that%20divides%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-class-flight-alaska-airlines-not-worth-it-basically-economy-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebusiness%20class%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20flight%20to%20Atlanta%2C%20though%2C%20the%20curtains%20were%20open%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20journey%2C%20which%20I%20didn't%20mind.%20It%20was%20quiet%20on%20the%20whole%20plane%20for%20much%20of%20the%20journey%20as%20people%20tried%20to%20sleep%2C%20and%20if%20I%20wanted%20silence%2C%20I%20could%20pop%20the%20provided%20earplugs%20into%20my%20ears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20my%20husband%20was%20sitting%20in%20economy%20(he%20joined%20me%20on%20my%20work%20trip%20on%20our%20dime%2C%20so%20we%20weren't%20able%20to%20swing%20a%20Delta%20One%20ticket%20for%20him)%2C%20and%20I%20liked%20that%20the%20open%20curtain%20allowed%20us%20to%20visit%20each%20other%20during%20the%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20AC%20felt%20better%20up%20front.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20woman%20with%20a%20blanket%20on%20a%20plane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b75aa6a17a8c5b4053e348%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Pettyjohn%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hadn't%20given%20much%20thought%20to%20how%20the%20plane's%20cooling%20system%20might%20differ%20between%20the%20Delta%20One%20cabin%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-is-the-best-place-to-sit-on-plane-worst-seats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20aircraft%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20my%20surprise%2C%20it%20felt%20cooler%20at%20the%20front%20of%20the%20plane.%20I%20had%20two%20personal%20air%20filters%20above%20my%20seat%2C%20when%20I%20only%20expected%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20also%20apparently%20flowed%20better%20in%20Delta%20One%20than%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20plane.%20While%20we%20were%20waiting%20on%20the%20tarmac%2C%20a%20flight%20attendant%20announced%20that%20they%20were%20adjusting%20the%20air%20to%20better%20cool%20the%20rear%20of%20the%20plane%2C%20where%20there%20were%20more%20passengers.%20My%20husband%20confirmed%20it%20had%20gotten%20pretty%20stuffy%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20my%20air%20was%20flowing%20so%20well%20that%20I%20had%20been%20planning%20to%20pull%20out%20my%20provided%20comforter%20for%20additional%20warmth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20flight%20attendants%20made%20dining%20an%20experience.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20business%20class%20meal%20on%20a%20Delta%20flight.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b75b42cfc04e97619c6f7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221139%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Pettyjohn%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20feeling%20I%20would%20be%20impressed%20by%20the%20food%20in%20Delta%20One%2C%20and%20the%20meal%20I%20had%20was%20certainly%20tastier%20than%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-private-jet-costs-own-charter-pilot-hangar-fuel-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eairplane%3C%2Fa%3E%20food%20I've%20eaten.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20more%20impressed%2C%20though%2C%20by%20the%20way%20the%20flight%20attendants%20elevated%20the%20dining%20experience%20in%20Delta%20One.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20they%20started%20serving%20food%2C%20a%20flight%20attendant%20spread%20out%20a%20cloth%20napkin%20on%20my%20tray%20table%20to%20keep%20the%20space%20clean.%20Everything%20was%20served%20in%20ceramic%20dishware%2C%20and%20the%20food%20was%20spaced%20out%20in%20courses%2C%20making%20me%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20in%20a%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmall%20touches%20like%20salt%20and%20pepper%20in%20a%20small%20shaker%20or%20a%20bottle%20of%20salad%20dressing%20instead%20of%20a%20packet%20also%20made%20the%20meal%20feel%20more%20luxurious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20warm%20cookie%20brought%20to%20me%20on%20a%20plate%20was%20my%20favorite%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20flight%20attendants%20attended%20to%20me%20even%20when%20I%20was%20sleeping.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221877%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20woman%20getting%20ready%20to%20sleep%20on%20a%20plane.%20She%20wears%20a%20face