ight%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Pettyjohn%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20had%20difficulty%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-sleeps-on-redeye-flights-overnight-trains-tips-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esleeping%20on%20planes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20was%20hopeful%20that%20my%20lie-flat%20seat%20might%20make%20it%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20my%20disappointment%2C%20I%20only%20slept%20for%20about%20two%20hours%20of%20my%20nine-hour%20flight%2C%20which%20was%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20time%20I%20slept%20on%20the%20journey%20to%20Europe%20when%20I%20was%20sitting%20in%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seat%20was%20comfortable%2C%20but%20other%20passengers%20and%20flight%20attendants%20moving%20around%20and%20the%20bumps%20of%20occasional%20turbulence%20kept%20me%20awake.%20It%20was%20still%20lovely%20to%20stretch%20my%20legs%20out%20and%20relax%2C%20even%20if%20sleep%20eluded%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20lastly%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20flying%20Delta%20One%20doesn't%20exempt%20you%20from%20some%20of%20the%20difficult%20parts%20of%20flying.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20TV%20screen%20on%20a%20plane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b75de8cfc04e97619c6fce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Pettyjohn%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20so%20excited%20to%20fly%20Delta%20One%20that%20I%20had%20no%20nerves%20about%20flying%20for%20nine%20hours.%20But%20the%20journey%20from%20Brussels%20to%20New%20York%20was%20actually%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20travel%20experiences%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%2010%3A45%20a.m.%20CET%20flight%20was%20first%20delayed%20about%2090%20minutes%20because%20the%20incoming%20flight%20was%20late.%20Once%20we%20boarded%2C%20we%20sat%20on%20the%20tarmac%20for%20four%20hours%20before%20taking%20off%20for%20the%20nine-hour%20flight%20because%20of%20a%20mechanical%20problem.%20I%20wasn't%20able%20to%20get%20on%20a%20connecting%20flight%20to%20New%20York%20until%2011%20p.m.%20ET%2C%20so%20I%20wasn't%20home%20until%20after%202%20a.m.%20I%20ended%20up%20traveling%20for%20a%20full%2024%20hours%20before%20I%20made%20it%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-premium-select-worth-it-business-class-alternative-long-flight-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDelta%20One%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20some%20of%20those%20stressors%20easier%2C%20as%20I%20was%20served%20additional%20snacks%20and%20beverages%20during%20the%20long%20wait%20on%20the%20tarmac%2C%20and%20I%20wasn't%20cramped%20in%20my%20seat%2C%20like%20some%20other%20passengers%20on%20the%20plane%20might%20have%20felt.%20It%20still%20wasn't%20fun%20to%20wait%20for%20so%20long%2C%20though%2C%20especially%20before%20a%20lengthy%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESitting%20in%20business%20class%20didn't%20mean%20the%20experience%20on%20board%20was%20perfect%20either.%20For%20instance%2C%20mine%20and%20several%20other%20passengers'%20TV%20screens%20weren't%20working%20when%20we%20boarded%2C%20and%20the%20flight%20attendants%20weren't%20able%20to%20fix%20them%20with%20a%20hard%20reset%20until%20we%20had%20been%20on%20the%20plane%20for%20over%20six%20hours.%20It%20wasn't%20anyone's%20fault%2C%20but%20it%20did%20make%20the%20lengthy%20time%20on%20the%20flight%20less%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelta%20people%20have%20the%20autonomy%20to%20offer%20on-the-spot%20service%20recovery%20in%20the%20uncommon%20event%20of%20inoperative%20in-flight%20entertainment%20or%20Wi-Fi%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Delta%20told%20Business%20Insider%20when%20contacted%20for%20this%20story.%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20customers%20can%20further%20contact%20Delta%20to%20have%20additional%20concerns%20heard%20and%20additional%20compensation%20may%20arrive%20on%20a%20case-by-case%20basis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20One%20offers%20a%20standout%20flight%20experience%2C%20but%20I'm%20glad%20I%20know%20now%20it%20won't%20make%20flying%20perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-one-international-flight-surprises-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757158141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b754baa17a8c5b4053e29f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-one-international-flight-surprises-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20sat%20in%20Delta's%20business%20class%20on%20a%20flight%20from%20Europe%20to%20the%20US.%20Delta%20One%20was%20amazing%2C%20but%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20some%20aspects%20of%20the%20journey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgrindell%40businessinsider.com%20(Samantha%20Grindell%20Pettyjohn)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-one-international-flight-surprises-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Bihar-Bidi%E2%80%99%20row%3A%20Kerala%20Cong%20admits%20'mistake'%3B%20social%20media%20head%20meets%20leaders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757157553000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-123734349%2Cimgsize-18188.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fbihar-bidi-post-row-kerala-congress-social-media-incharge-vt-balram-resigns%2Farticleshow%2F123734085.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20controversy%20erupted%20after%20Kerala%20Congress's%20social%20media%20post%20compared%20Bihar%20to%20a%20'bidi'%2C%20drawing%20criticism%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20upsetting%20ally%20RJD.%20The%20post%2C%20a%20dig%20at%20GST%20rates%2C%20was%20deleted%2C%20and%20an%20apolog