nd%20of%20frustrations%20for%20American%20small%20businesses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Container%20ship%20MSC%20Ronit%20R%20docks%20in%20Newark%20after%20arriving%20from%20France%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b8ad6032af4d666ef73266%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20end%20of%20a%20long-standing%20duty%20exemption%20for%20low-value%20items%20is%20creating%20chaos%20and%20shipping%20difficulties%20for%20small%20American%20businesses.%3Cp%3EEduardo%20Munoz%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20end%20of%20the%20de%20minimis%20exemption%20is%20creating%20chaos%20at%20customs%20and%20shipping%20suspensions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusinesses%20that%20rely%20on%20small%20batch%20imports%20are%20scrambling%20to%20contend%20with%20increasing%20duties.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERetail%20analysts%20anticipate%20higher%20and%20stickier%20prices%20and%20more%20consumer%20cutbacks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20end%20of%20a%20long-standing%20duty%20exemption%20for%20low-value%20items%20is%20creating%20chaos%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmain-street-trump-trade-war-tariffs-small-businesses-impact-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esmall%20American%20businesses%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeri%20Olson%2C%20founder%20of%20Diesel%20and%20Lulu's%2C%20a%20boutique%20business%20that%20brings%20seasonal%20premium%20European%20apparel%20to%20US%20shoppers%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20feels%20like%20her%20goods%20are%20facing%20a%20%26quot%3Bhostage%20situation%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20customs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fde-minimis-how-tariff-change-small-packages-affects-your-orders-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ede%20minimis%20exemption%3C%2Fa%3E%20used%20to%20allow%20goods%20under%20%24800%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20duty-free%20and%20with%20minimal%20paperwork.%20But%20since%20it%20ended%20on%20August%2029%2C%20Olson's%20small-batch%20imports%20from%20Europe%20are%20facing%20duties%20she%20could%20not%20predict%20based%20on%20nuanced%20material%20and%20provincial%20differences%20in%20the%20customs%20code.%20These%20duties%20are%20on%20top%20of%20the%20existing%20tariffs%20the%20Trump%20administration%20has%20imposed%20on%20the%20EU%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOlson%20said%20that%20her%20most%20recent%20order%20from%20a%20small%20European%20vendor%20is%20worth%20%24660.%20Not%20only%20has%20the%20shipping%20cost%20gone%20up%20from%20%2490%20to%20%24150%20compared%20to%20a%20previous%20order%20of%20similar%20weight%20and%20value%2C%20but%20she%20is%20also%20facing%20a%20duty%20of%20%24251.%20Vendors%20are%20also%20not%20responsible%20for%20refunds%20should%20the%20receiver%20be%20unable%20to%20pay%20the%20duty%2C%20and%20the%20item%20gets%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20taking%20it%20day%20by%20day%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Olson%2C%20whose%20boutique%20has%20expanded%20to%20six%20locations%20across%20the%20country%20since%20its%20establishment%20in%202012%20in%20Cape%20Cod%20in%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20absorb%20a%20good%20deal%20of%20the%20costs%20while%20we%20wait%20it%20out%20to%20see%20what%20happens%2C%20but%20we%20can't%20absorb%20it%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Olson%20added.%20%26quot%3BIf%20my%20business%20were%20to%20fold%2C%20you're%20talking%20about%20the%20impacts%20on%20all%20of%20the%20employees%2C%20the%20artists%20we%20work%20with%2C%20and%20our%20philanthropic%20activities%20like%20fundraisers%20for%20individual%20families%20and%20animals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fde-minimis-how-tariff-change-small-packages-affects-your-orders-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ede%20minimis%20threshold%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20part%20of%20US%20customs%20since%20the%201930s%2C%20and%20it%20has%20stood%20at%20%24800%20since%202016.%20The%20duty-free%20shipments%20ceased%20first%20for%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20China%20on%20May%202%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20on%20August%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20end%20of%20the%20exemption%2C%20over%2030%20countries'%20main%20postal%20services%2C%20including%20Norway%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Denmark%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsome-european-postal-services-sellers-are-suspending-us-bound-shipments-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etemporarily%20suspended%20shipments%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20US%2C%20citing%20their%20inability%20to%20process%20prepaid%20duties%2C%20customs%20paperwork%2C%20and%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20postal%20services%2C%20such%20as%20the%20British%20Royal%20Mail%2C%20have%20resorted%20to%20a%20hefty%20flat%20fee%20for%20handling%20US-bound%20parcels%20for%20at%20least%20half%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e448790b-17db-479d-bc47-0e6cb2af6085%5C%22%3EConsumers%20may%20face%20permanently%20higher%20price%20points%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20and%20business%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20survival%20of%20small%20businesses%20and%20the%20impact%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-consumer-confidence-corporate-earnings-outlook-risk-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsumer%20sentiment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacob%20Bennett%2C%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20small%20business%20banking%20platform%20Crux%20Analytics%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20is%20seeing%20a%20spike%20in%20searches%20for%20information%20on%20how%20to%20access%20emergency%20business%20funding%2C%20cover%20unexpected%20costs%2C%20and%20wind%20down%20or%20close%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBennett%20pointed%20to%20data%20from%20the%20American%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20that%20small%20businesses%20employ%20nearly%20half%20of%20the%20American%20workforce%20and%20contribute%20more%20than%2040%25%20of%20the%20country's%20GDP%2C%20and%20said%20that%20the%20downstream%20effect%20of%20the%20burden%20on%20smaller%20businesses%20will%20begin%20to%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSmall%20businesses%20are%20the%20first%20to%20feel%20the%20effect%2C%20and%20they%20feel%20it%20the%20most%20acutely%2C%20but%20that%20effect%20does%20trickle%20down%20to%20the%20wider%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bennett.%20%26quot%3BThe%20point%20isn't%20that%20change%20is%20bad%20necessarily%2C%20it's%20that%20change%20needs%20to%20be%20thoughtful%2C%20and%20the%20transition%20needs%20to%20be%20reasonable%20in%20terms%20of%20timeline%20and%20speed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartin%20Balaam%2C%20CEO%20of%20Pimberly%2C%20a%20product%20data%20management%20platform%20for%20global%20retail%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20businesses%20tend%20to%20adapt%20over%20time%2C%20but%20prices%20will%20become%20sticky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-temu-wont-be-killed-by-de-minimis-exemption-changes-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShein%20and%20Temu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20vast%20amount%20of%20small%20parcel%20shipments%20to%20the%20US%20originally%20drew%20attention%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20duties%2C%20figured%20out%20a%20workaround%20by%20bulk%20shipping%20to%20the%20US%20before%20redistributing%20the%20items%20to%20avoid%20duties%20on%20individual%20packages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20paperwork%20sounds%20difficult%20now%2C%20but%20this%20will%20get%20normalized%2C%20and%20ultimately%20you'll%20still%20be%20left%20with%20the%20increased%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Balaam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20that%20US%20consumers%20understand%20that%20it's%20not%20fair%20for%20the%20domestic%20market%20for%20other%20countries%20to%20have%20a%20fast-track%20express%2C%20duty-free%20methodology%20of%20delivering%20and%20selling%20their%20goods%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Balaam%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-raising-prices-increases-trump-tariffs-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprice%20inflation%3C%2Fa%3E%20starts%20coming%20through%2C%20they'll%20probably%20not%20be%20too%20happy%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-end-of-de-minimis-creating-chaos-for-small-businesses-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757156642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b8ae2cf9db348adc0ac7f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-end-of-de-minimis-creating-chaos-for-small-businesses-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Small%20businesses%20are%20facing%20hefty%20customs%20bills%20and%20soaring%20shipping%20costs%20after%20a%20long-standing%20duty%20exemption%20on%20low-value%20parcels%20ended%20in%20August.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Li)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-end-of-de-minimis-creating-chaos-for-small-businesses-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sudanese%20villagers%20dig%20with%20hands%20to%20reach%20landslide%20victims%2C%20group%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757156558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F4897%2Flive%2Fb220ae40-8b0c-11f0-9a92-61c69444c65a.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn0xepvr0x4o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22People%20have%20no%20access%20to%20tools%20or%20machinery%20to%20conduct%20their%20rescue%20efforts%2C%20Save%20the%20Children%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22e