20Nathaneo%20Johnson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20might%20wonder%20how%20I%20find%20the%20time%20to%20build%20Series%20as%20a%20senior%20at%20Yale.%20But%20being%20a%20student%20is%20easy%3A%20you%20just%20go%20to%20class%20and%20pass.%20The%20time%20that%20students%20put%20into%20extracurricular%20activities%2C%20their%20friendship%20groups%2C%20and%20so%20many%20other%20minuscule%20time%20commitments%2C%20I%20spend%20on%20my%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20normally%20spend%20about%2018%20hours%20a%20day%20in%20my%20office%2C%20often%20working%20for%20120%20hours%20a%20week%20on%20a%20mix%20of%20college%20work%20and%20startup%20stuff.%20The%20key%20thing%20is%20time%20management.%20It's%20about%20being%20disciplined%20and%20organized%20and%20delegating%20when%20you%20can.%20If%20you%20can't%20delegate%20to%20others%2C%20then%20it's%20about%20prioritization%20and%20sacrificing%20more.%20That's%20how%20to%20best%20position%20yourself%20to%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20moment%2C%20I'm%20doing%20a%20lot%20at%20college.%20We're%20about%20to%20head%20into%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpitch-deck-ai-agent-startup-artisan-series-a-funding-round-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESeries%20A%20funding%3C%2Fa%3E%20pretty%20soon.%20Yet%2C%20I'm%20feeling%20euphoric.%20There's%20nothing%20better%20than%20living%20your%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20working%20in%20AI%20during%20or%20straight%20after%20college%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzitser%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejzitser%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnathaneo-johnson-yale-student-series-raised-million-ai-startup-time-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3