soup%20or%20salad%2C%20and%20breadsticks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20here%2C%20you're%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20we%20apparently%20live%20under%20an%20enormous%20rock%2C%20neither%20of%20us%20had%20been%20part%20of%20the%20fabled%20Olive%20Garden%20family%20until%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%20We%20went%20for%20the%20cheap%2C%20bottomless%20entr%C3%A9es%2C%20but%20we%20had%20no%20idea%20the%20high%20prices%20our%20stomachs%20would%20pay%20to%20be%20welcomed%20into%20said%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20just%20brought%20back%20its%20hit%20promotion%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folive-gardens-never-ending-pasta-bowl-may-not-return-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Never-Ending%20Pasta%20Bowl%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20run%20from%20August%2025%20to%20November.%20The%20deal%2C%20which%20starts%20at%20%2413.99%2C%20lets%20you%20mix%20and%20match%20your%20favorite%20pastas%2C%20sauces%2C%20and%20proteins%20%E2%80%94%20it%20also%20comes%20with%20soup%20or%20salad%2C%20plus%20breadsticks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20special's%20price%20has%20stayed%20the%20same%20since%202022%2C%20despite%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20with%20an%20optimism%20we%20would%20quickly%20learn%20was%20woefully%20misguided%2C%20we%20set%20out%20to%20push%20ourselves%20%3Cem%3Epasta%3C%2Fem%3E%20our%20limits%20(sorry).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20journey%20begins%20in%20Times%20Square.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221658%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Olive%20Garden%20signs%20in%20Times%20Square%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68baeca3f9db348adc0ae690%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221222%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20Jackson%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20options%20in%20New%20York%20City%20seem%20infinite%20sometimes.%20You%20can%20step%20outside%20your%20front%20door%20and%20stumble%20across%20a%20hidden%20culinary%20gem.%20There%20are%20also%20times%20when%20an%20affordable%20bowl%20of%20pasta%20from%20a%20staple%20restaurant%20chain%20requires%20a%2040-minute%20train%20ride%20and%20the%20overwhelming%20foot%20traffic%20of%20Times%20Square.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUndeterred%2C%20we%20eventually%20made%20it%20to%20our%20destination%3A%20The%20only%20Olive%20Garden%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOne%20extremely%20long%20escalator%20ride%20later%2C%20we%20arrived%20at%20our%20booth.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22924%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Olive%20Garden%20menu%20reading%20%26quot%3BBenvenuto%20-%20Welcome%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68baf17532af4d666ef7519b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221244%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20Jackson%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20seated%20with%20the%20standard%20menu%2C%20which%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20never-ending%20pasta%20promotion.%20We%20asked%20our%20waitress%20when%20she%20arrived%2C%20and%20she%20returned%20with%20a%20slip%20of%20paper%20for%20each%20of%20us%20that%20laid%20out%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOh%2C%20the%20pastabilities%20are%20endless!%20(Well%2C%20technically%2C%20there's%20around%20100.)%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22688%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Olive%20Garden%20never-ending%20pasta%20bowl%20promotion%20menu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68baf28957d362d375e79774%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221020%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20Jackson%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20tough%20parts%20about%20eating%20in%20an%20area%20dense%20with%20tourists%20is%20the%20high%20pricing.%20The%20never-ending%20pasta%20deal%20usually%20starts%20at%20%2413.99%20per%20person%2C%20but%20for%20this%20Times%20Square%20location%2C%20it%20was%20%2419.99%20%E2%80%94%20plus%20an%20extra%20%245.99%20to%20add%20unlimited%20protein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20waitress%20quickly%20brought%20us%20breadsticks.%20Sarah%20started%20with%20the%20Pasta%20e%20Fagioli%20soup%2C%20and%20Jordan%20got%20the%20house%20salad.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221626%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Olive%20Garden%20soup%20and%20salad%20before%20never-ending%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bb342a57d362d375e7a491%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221168%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20were%20sizable%20portions%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20make%20much%20progress%20on%20either%20to%20save%20space%20for%20the%20pastas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFor%20our%20first%20pasta%20order%2C%20Jordan%20got%20fettuccine%20Alfredo%20with%20chicken%20fritta.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Olive%20Garden%20fettuccine%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bb13c957d362d375e79dcc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20size%20of%20our%20first%20portion%20was%20daunting%2C%20but%20my%20first%20bite%20was%20delicious%20and%20creamy.%20I%20immediately%20knew%20that%20the%20crispy%20chicken%20would%20be%20my%20favorite%20protein.%20Spoiler%20alert%3A%20I%20was%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20my%20first%20plate%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20was%20in%20trouble.%20Starting%20with%20a%20cream-based%20Alfredo%20sauce%20and%20breaded%20chicken%20was%20a%20risk.%20The%20heaviness%20worried%20me.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20determined%20to%20keep%20pushing%20on%20to%20the%20next%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESarah's%20first%20pasta%20was%20spaghetti%20with%20the%20new%20spicy%20meat%20sauce.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Olive%20Garden%20never-ending%20pasta%20spaghetti%20with%20spicy%20meat%20sauce%20and%20a%20meatball%20and%20sausage%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bb1091f9db348adc0aece4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221216%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20Jackson%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20spice%20fiend%2C%20the%20spicy%20sauce%20was%20a%20no-brainer.%20I%20initially%20wanted%20to%20get%20angel%20hair%20for%20my%20first%20round%20since%20it%20seems%20lighter%2C%20and%20we%20have%20to%20pace%20ourselves%20(this%20is%20a%20pasta%20marathon%2C%20not%20a%20sprint%2C%20after%20all).%20In%20the%20end%2C%20though%2C%20I%20went%20with%20the%20classic%20spaghetti.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20indecisive%20about%20the%20meat%20option%2C%20but%20our%20waitress%20mentioned%20they%20could%20serve%20one%20meatball%20and%20one%20sausage%20%E2%80%94%20decision%20paralysis%20solved!%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20hadn't%20realized%20the%20first%20pasta%20dish%20was%20the%20largest%2C%20and%20subsequent%20ones%20were%20all%20smaller.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221044%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Olive%20Garden%20never-ending%20pasta%20angel%20hair%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bb33d432af4d666ef75ee4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22970%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20started%20with%20a%20tomato-based%20sauce%20and%20mostly%20ate%20the%20sauce%2C%20avoiding%20the%20pasta%20(strategically%2C%20but%20ironically%20given%20the%20name%20of%20the%20deal)%20to%20save%20room.%20As%20Jordan%20later%20commented%20on%20Sarah's%20first%20round%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20pasta%20left%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20call%20you%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%2C%20having%20started%20with%20a%20heavier%20cream-based%20sauce%2C%20was%20starting%20to%20have%20regrets.%20When