20fresh%2C%20empty-stomached%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20asked%20our%20waitress%20about%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20never-ending%20pasta%20deal%2C%20and%20she%20said%20most%20tables%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20offer%20when%20it's%20available.%20The%20day%20before%20our%20visit%2C%20she%20said%20she%20waited%20on%20one%20customer%20who%20made%20it%20through%20a%20whopping%2010%20bowls.%20She%20said%2C%20on%20average%2C%20customers%20make%20it%20through%20around%206%20bowls.%20That%E2%80%A6was%20absolutely%20astonishing%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20round%20three%2C%20Jordan%20got%20the%20gluten-free%20rotini%20with%20marinara%2C%20sans%20protein.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Olive%20Garden%20marinara%20pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bb12e6f9db348adc0aed67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222826%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20usually%20go%20for%20a%20gluten-free%20option.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20trying%20all%20of%20the%20available%20pasta%20shapes%2C%20I%20gave%20it%20a%20try.%20The%20sauce%20was%20lighter%20than%20the%20Alfredo%20and%20five-cheese%20marinara%2C%20and%20it%20had%20that%20juicy%20tomato%20flavor%20I%20was%20hoping%20for.%20The%20rotini%20was%20quite%20chewy%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ditched%20the%20protein%20this%20round%20in%20the%20hopes%20that%20it%20would%20help%20me%20finish%20more%20of%20my%20bowl.%20It%20didn't%20help%20much.%20I%20ended%20up%20picking%20at%20it%2C%20eating%20one%20noodle%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20taking%20breaks%20from%20eating%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESarah%20got%20the%20angel%20hair%20Alfredo%20with%20chicken%20again.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221632%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Olive%20Garden%20never-ending%20pasta%20angel%20hair%20Alfredo%20with%20chicken%20