20obstacles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESuch%20a%20move%20could%20also%20bring%20opportunities%20to%20expand%20CBS%20News%20beyond%20linear%20TV.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20would%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftucker-carlson-megyn-kelly-bari-weiss-youtube-podcasts-chris-balfe-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBari%20Weiss%3C%2Fa%3E%20era%20at%20CBS%20News%20look%20like%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20question%20has%20been%20pondered%20this%20week%20across%20drinks%20and%20in%20text%20chains%20in%20the%20media%20world.%20The%20catalyst%3A%20reports%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpuck.news%2Fdavid-ellison-set-to-acquire-the-free-press%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPuck%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20outlets%20that%20Paramount%20Skydance%20is%20closing%20in%20on%20a%20deal%20to%20buy%20Weiss'%20news%20startup%20The%20Free%20Press%20and%20install%20her%20in%20a%20leadership%20role%20at%20CBS%20News.%20Paramount%20and%20The%20Free%20Press%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShaking%20up%20CBS%20News%20has%20been%20a%20stated%20%E2%80%94%20if%20nebulous%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0goal%20of%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-ufc-rights-tko-deal-david-ellison-netflix-streaming-wars-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EParamount%20chief%20David%20Ellison%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20Ellison%20met%20the%20press%20in%20August%20after%20the%20merger%20of%20Paramount%20and%20Skydance%2C%20he%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20reach%20as%20wide%20an%20audience%20as%20possible%20with%20CBS%20News%20and%20that%20there%20were%20areas%20where%20the%20newsroom%20could%20%26quot%3Bdo%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20without%20offering%20specifics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeiss%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-times-editor-bari-weiss-resigns-letter-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleft%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020%20with%20a%20public%2C%20anti-woke%20resignation%20letter%2C%20could%20inject%20a%20different%20sensibility%20into%20CBS%20News.%20She's%20known%20for%20bucking%20liberal%20and%20conservative%20orthodoxy%20and%20taking%20strong%20stances%20on%20particular%20topics%20like%20Israel%20and%20college-campus%20speech.%20If%20Weiss%20tried%20to%20push%20more%20commentary%20into%20the%20equation%2C%20she%20could%20face%20resistance%20at%20the%20network%20known%20for%20its%20iconic%20straight-news%20program%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes.%26quot%3B%20It%20also%20might%20not%20work%20for%20the%20audience%20and%20advertisers%20trying%20to%20reach%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrying%20to%20broaden%20your%20audience%20by%20bringing%20in%20different%20points%20of%20view%20is%20rarely%20successful%2C%20particularly%20with%20network%20news%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cathy%20Rasenberger%2C%20a%20TV%20industry%20consultant.%20%26quot%3BThe%20median%20age%20for%20network%20news%20is%2065.%20They're%20very%20loyal%20to%20their%20particular%20source%20of%20news%2C%20and%20when%20they%20feel%20that%20the%20source%20is%20disloyal%2C%20they'll%20switch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETV%20insiders%20and%20analysts%20said%20Weiss'%20biggest%20potential%20value%20would%20be%20in%20helping%20CBS%20News%20improve%20its%20digital%20chops%20and%20reach%20a%20younger%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllie%20Kosterich%2C%20a%20communications%20professor%20at%20Fordham%20University%2C%20said%20there%20could%20be%20upside%20in%20expanding%20CBS%20News'%20streaming%20footprint%2C%20helped%20by%20The%20Free%20Press'%20personality-driven%20programming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Free%20Press%20has%20amassed%201.5%20million%20subscribers%2C%20including%20about%20170%2C000%20paying%20ones%2C%20and%20also%20reaches%20people%20through%20live%20events%2C%20podcasts%2C%20and%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKosterich%20said%20she%20sees%20opinion-led%20content%20helmed%20by%20Weiss%20working%20well%20as%20livestreams%20and%20clips%20on%20platforms%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22