lk%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20Insider%3A%20You%20use%20a%20flip%20phone%3F%20Tell%20me%20about%20that.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGraham%3A%20I%20had%20%5Ba%20smartphone%5D%20briefly%20after%20college%2C%20and%20then%20when%20I%20started%20the%20business%2C%20I%20went%20to%20a%20flip%20phone.%20I've%20never%20really%20had%20social%20media.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20was%20just%20so%20simple.%20I've%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20views%20on%20technology%2C%20obviously%2C%20and%20it's%20all%20bound%20up%20in%20the%20business%20and%20creating%20boundaries%20and%20how%20I%20think%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20Yondr%2C%20my%20hypothesis%20was%20that%20to%20be%20a%20person%20in%20the%20world%20walking%20around%20with%20a%20computer%20in%20your%20pocket%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20radically%20different%20human%20experience%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20younger%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20for%20me%2C%20as%20a%20person%2C%20I%20just%20prefer%20to%20have%20fewer%20inputs.%20It's%20that%20simple.%20It%20just%20simplifies%20my%20life.%20Everything%20I%20do%20is%20long-form%20conversation%2C%20and%20that%20works%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'd%20imagine%20a%20CEO%20would%20need%20constant%20access%20to%20email%20or%20DocuSign%20or%20whatnot.%20But%20you%20really%20walk%20the%20walk%2C%20huh%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20funny%20thing%20about%20technology%20is%20that%20the%20work%20expands%20to%20fill%20the%20time%20allotted.%20The%20modern%20work%20style%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0everything%20being%20connected%20everywhere%20all%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0makes%20certain%20things%20more%20efficient%2C%20but%20it%20tends%20to%20just%20bleed%20out%20decisions%20into%20infinite%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20create%20structure%20around%20things%2C%20it%20forces%20you%20to%20make%20decisions%20in%20certain%20time%20frames.%20Once%20you%20leave%20the%20office%2C%20you%20can't%20sign%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETechnology%20doesn't%20really%20knock%20at%20the%20door%20and%20ask%20permission%20to%20enter.%20Once%20you%20open%20up%20the%20phone%20or%20you%20enter%20into%20a%20medium%2C%20you're%20playing%20by%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20game%20that%20are%20pre-configured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22teesn%20hold%20yondr%20pouches%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bb4e3e32af4d666ef7643b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStudents%20use%20Yondr%20pouches%20for%20their%20phones%20during%20school.%3Cp%3EGenaro%20Molina%2FLos%20Angeles%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMost%20people%20seem%20to%20think%20it's%20common%20sense%20to%20ban%20phones%2C%20but%20then%20I%20also%20heard%20from%20a%20mom%20who%20said%20her%20teen%20just%20started%20school%20with%20a%20phone%20ban%2C%20and%20there's%20been%20all%20these%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20so%20much%20that's%20baked%20into%20the%20school%20that%20assumes%20kids%20have%20phones.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20theatre%20club%20signup%20requires%20scanning%20a%20QR%20code.%20Is%20Yondr%20going%20to%20be%20changing%20how%20schools%20are%20run%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20go%20back%20to%202014%2C%20when%20our%20team%20was%20out%20knocking%20on%20doors%20and%20talking%20about%20a%20phone-free%20school%2C%20remember%20the%20idea%20didn't%20exist%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20something%20we%20had%20invented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20at%20that%20time%2C%20the%20answer%20I%20got%20from%20most%20people%20was%20%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20get%20more%20tech%20into%20the%20classroom%2C%20not%20less.%26quot%3B%20The%20zeitgeist%20has%20changed%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20your%20question%20about%20the%20infrastructure%20and%20what%20a%20school%20ecosystem%20looks%20like%2C%20that's%20probably%20the%20biggest%20part%20of%20what%20we%20do%20as%20a%20company.%20When%20people%20think%20of%20Yondr%2C%20they'll%20think%20of%20just%20the%20pouch.%20What%20they%20don't%20always%20realize%20is%20that%20a%20big%20part%20of%20what%20we%20do%20is%20go%20in%2C%20we're%20helping%20get%20the%20parents%20on%20board%20with%20the%20idea%20that%20includes%20how%20they%20interact%20with%20their%20school%20and%20communicate%20throughout%20the%20day.%20We're%20actually%20helping%20the%20teachers%20and%20unwinding%20some%20of%20those%20learned%20behaviors%20that%20have%20kind%20of%20built%20up%20around%20that%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there's%20the%20ongoing%20support%20because%20it's%20a%20cultural%20and%20an%20etiquette%20change%20inside%20of%20a%20school.%20Just%20introducing%20a%20tool%20is%20not%20enough.%20You%20have%20to%20start%20to%20unwind%20some%20of%20the%20things%20that%20are%20prohibiting%20schools%20from%20being%20able%20to%20create%20a%20phone-free%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20of%20that%2C%20the%20other%20things%20you%20talked%20about%2C%20sign-ins%20and%20some%20of%20the%20more%20tech%20solutions%20to%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20become%20just%20so%20much%20more%20complicated%20and%20time-consuming%20than%20just%20writing%20your%20name%20on%20a%20clipboard.%20It's%20funny%20to%20look%20at%20those%20things%20and%20go%3A%20%3Cem%3EAre%20those%20tools%20actually%20that%20helpful%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20protect%20your%20business%20from%20another%20company%20coming%20along%20and%20making%20pouches%20that%20are%20just%2020%25%20cheaper%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20just%20ship%20pouches%20to%20a%20school.%20We%20have%20a%20whole%20arm%20of%20the%20company%20that's%20all%20former%20educators.%20It%20helps%20with%20the%20implementation%2C%20the%20rollout%2C%20the%20policy%20creation%2C%20and%20the%20planning.%20So%20there's%20the%20pre-launch%20board%2C%20the%20logistics%2C%20and%20the%20policy.%20There's%20the%20actual%20implementation%2C%20which%20we%20help%20with%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20then%20the%20ongoing%20support%20in%20the%20evaluation%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20ever%20run%20into%20teenagers%20who%20are%20like%2C%20%3Cem%3EYou're%20ruining%20my%20life.%20I%20hate%20your%20stupid%20pouches%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOh%2C%20definitely.%20I%20get%20all%20sorts%20of%20interesting%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20there%20ever%20positive%20ones%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20hundred%20percent.%20We%20sometimes%20get%20whole%20essay-length%20messages%20from%20students%20saying%20what%20the%20effect%20of%20a%20phone-free%20school%20has%20had%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20young%20people%20%3Cem%3Eknow%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20on%20their%20phone%20as%20much%2C%20or%20have%20a%20feeling%20that%20%3Cem%3Emaybe%20being%20online%20all%20the%20time%20is%20not%20helpful.%20%3C%2Fem%3ESo%20our%20goal%20is%20just%20to%20be%20like%2C%20%3Cem%3EHey%2C%20that's%20great.%20Maybe%20a%20phone-free%20space%20is%20helpful%20to%20you%3C%2Fem%3E.%20And%20as%20you%20get%20older%2C%20you%20can%20decide%20what%20to%20do%20with%20that%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20have%20any%20digital%20indulgences%3F%20Like%2C%20you're%20completely%20addicted%20to%20Strava%2C%20or%20can't%20stop%20watching%20TikToks%20about%20fishing%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20to%20watch%20tennis%20highlights%20on%20YouTube.%20I'm%20a%20big%20tennis%20fan%2C%20so%20that's%20my%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat's%20pretty%20tame.%20It's%20like%20saying%2C%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BMy%20diet%20weakness%20is%20carrot%20sticks%3C%2Fem%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELook%2C%20I%20find%20social%20media%20so%20fundamentally%20lame%2C%20I%20just%20can't%20describe%20it%20to%20you.%20It%20doesn't%20seem%20like%20any%20fun%20to%20me%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20really%20tell%20you%20much%20about%20how%20people%20are%20or%20what's%20really%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20what%20I%20love%20about%20a%20phone-free%20concert%20or%20show%20when%20we%20do%20them.%20All%20these%20people%20spend%20all%20the%20time%20online%20developing%20preconceptions%20and%20associations%20with%20things%20at%20this%20highly%20amalgamated%2C%20weird%20level.%20Then%2C%20they%20go%20to%20a%20concert%20and%20it's%20phone-free%20and%20people%20are%20bumping%20into%20each%20other%20and%20talking%20at%20the%20concession%20stands%2C%20and%20they're%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20great%20artist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20very%20humanizing%20effect%20on%20people%2C%20and%20it's%20very%20healthy%20for%20civil%20society.%20That's%20why%20we%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyondr-ceo-graham-dugoni-phone-pouch-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757149321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bb541df9db348adc0afa82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyondr-ceo-graham-dugoni-phone-pouch-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yondr%20makes%20the%20zippered%20pouches%20for%20phone-free%20zones%2C%20like%20schools%20and%20concerts.%20We%20asked%20the%20CEO%20about%20social%20media%20%E2%80%94%20and%20why%20he%20uses%20a%20flip%20phone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyondr-ceo-graham-dugoni-phone-pouch-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Who%20drafted%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20X%20post%3F'%3A%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20hits%20out%20at%20deputy%20CM%20over%20viral%20video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757149268000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https