many%20questions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20clear%20to%20him%20that%20the%20blueprint%20of%20a%20well-adjusted%20human%20being%20is%20laid%20out%20in%20the%20early%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20six%20to%20eight%20years%20of%20our%20lives%20matter%20the%20most%20as%20the%20first%20%E2%80%98AI%20model%E2%80%99%20of%20our%20brain%20is%20written%20without%20our%20consent.%20Children%20just%20become%20what%20they%20see%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%20emphatically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20started%20sharing%20his%20understanding%20of%20parenting%20on%20social%20media%20and%20why%20children%20behave%20a%20certain%20way.%20With%20parents%20leading%20busy%20lives%2C%20Harpreet%20wishes%20to%20help%20them%20through%20his%20five-minute%20videos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Parents%2C%20observe%20from%20a%20distance%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChildren%20don%E2%80%99t%20come%20with%20a%20manual.%20Earlier%2C%20people%20would%20say%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Bacche%20aise%20hi%20bade%20ho%20jayenge%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333887%2Fsangopita-shelter-home-disabled-children-cerebral-palsy-autism-adhd%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChildren%20grow%20up%20automatically%3C%2Fa%3E).%20Yes%2C%20but%20will%20they%20grow%20up%20properly%3F%20That%20is%20why%20I%20want%20parents%20to%20observe%20their%20children.%20Think%20about%20%3Cem%3Ewhy%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethey%20are%20doing%20what%20they%20are%20doing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013-1756995112-500x684.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013-1756995112-500x684.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013-1756995112-219x300.jpeg%20219w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013-1756995112-768x1051.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013-1756995112-150x205.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-20-at-14.20.59-1724423013-1756995112.jpeg%20830w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496544%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22684%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%20changed%20Harpreet%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20his%20daughter%20greatly%2C%20who%20spent%20the%20first%20two%20years%20of%20her%20life%20in%20a%20daycare.%20But%20after%20she%20turned%20three%20and%20started%20attending%20school%2C%20Harpreet%20made%20sure%20that%20all%20his%20time%20was%20spent%20with%20her.%20Another%20thing%20he%20changed%20was%20staying%20away%20from%20the%20carrot%20and%20stick%20approach%20(using%20rewards%20and%20punishment%20to%20encourage%20desired%20behaviour%20which%20most%20of%20us%20are%20accustomed%20to).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20argues%20that%20every%20child%20is%20inherently%20motivated%20to%20grow%20and%20that%20if%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20offer%20them%20a%20reward%20to%20walk%20or%20talk%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20do%20the%20same%20for%20any%20other%20task.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20reflects%20on%20whether%20we%20need%20to%20put%20children%20in%20so%20many%20classes%20and%20if%20they%20really%20enjoy%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20give%20our%20child%20the%20space%20to%20find%20what%20they%20like.%20We%20need%20to%20give%20them%20exposure%20to%20understand%20what%20they%20like.%20It%20has%20taken%20me%2040%20years%20to%20come%20to%20a%20place%20where%20I%E2%80%99m%20doing%20something%20I%20love.%20I%20am%20internally%20motivated%20today%2C%20nobody%20is%20pushing%20me.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20doing%20it%20for%20fame%2C%20money%20or%20external%20validation.%20I%E2%80%99m%20doing%20it%20because%20I%20love%20doing%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarpreet%20points%20out%20that%20we%20need%20to%20teach%20children%20to%20regulate%20their%20emotions.%20Hitting%20obviously%20is%20not%20the%20right%20way%20to%20do%20it%2C%20nor%20is%20propping%20them%20up%20before%20a%20screen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20they%20are%2030%20and%20angry%2C%20are%20they%20going%20to%20see%20a%20screen%20and%20pacify%20themselves%3F%20We%20should%20not%20teach%20children%20to%20distract%20themselves%20because%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20help%20them%20process%20their%20emotions.%20Just%20because%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20taught%20this%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20we%20should%20repeat%20it%20with%20the%20next%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20child%20is%20watching%20a%20screen%2C%20they%20are%20not%20involved%20in%20anything%20around%20them.%20That%20is%20the%20core%20issue%20which%20leads%20to%20many%20mental%20health%20problems.%20To%20prevent%20this%2C%20we%20need%20to%20involve%20children%20in%20a%20daily%20routine%20doing%20household%20chores%2C%20take%20them%20outside%2C%20and%20build%20a%20community%20of%20friends%20for%20them%20to%20play%20with.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20keep%20children%20involved%20in%20purposeful%20work%20which%20also%20fosters%20empathy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-32-1724422779.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-32-1724422779.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-32-1724422779-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-32-1724422779-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-32-1724422779-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FInfographic-website-32-1724422779-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362808%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEmotions%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20replaced%20with%20mobile%20phones%20or%20screens%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20parents%2C%20Harpreet%20offers%20a%20few%20basic%20pieces%20of%20advice%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Parenting%20is%20not%20about%20the%20child%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20videos%20on%20parenting%2C%20Harpreet%20also%20offers%20two%20courses%2C%20one%20on%20%E2%80%98understanding%20your%20child%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20other%20on%20%E2%80%98how%20to%20select%20a%20school%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSchool%20is%20a%20preparation%20for%20life.%20Find%20a%20school%20where%20mistakes%20are%20allowed.%20There%20is%20no%20one%C2%A0special%20school%20which%20can%20make%20your%20child%20super%20successful.%20A%20school%20should%20have%20a%20loving%20and%20caring%20environment%20where%