%80%9D%20Harsh%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CInstalling%20rooftop%20solar%20meant%20discarding%20your%20existing%20inverter%20and%20buying%20a%20new%2C%20solar-compatible%20one.%20It%20was%20unaffordable%20for%20most%20families%20and%20created%20huge%20amounts%20of%20e-waste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20challenge%20sparked%20an%20idea.%20Guided%20by%20his%20professor%20Dr%20Vinod%20Gopal%2C%20Harsh%20began%20tinkering%20with%20a%20solution%3A%20What%20if%2C%20instead%20of%20replacing%20inverters%2C%20they%20could%20create%20a%20small%20device%20that%20connected%20any%20inverter%20to%20solar%20panels%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReiterating%20this%20idea%2C%20Nishanth%20CP%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Energy24by7%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%20way%2C%20households%20could%20adopt%20solar%20without%20buying%20a%20new%20system%2C%20reducing%20both%20costs%20and%20pollution.%20Our%20aim%20was%20to%20make%20solar%20accessible%20to%20middle-class%20families%2C%20not%20just%20the%20wealthy.%20Back%20then%2C%20panels%20were%20very%20expensive%2C%20and%20people%20thought%20solar%20was%20only%20for%20the%20rich.%20We%20wanted%20to%20change%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20device%20became%20%E2%80%98iCON%E2%80%99%20(Intelligent%20Converter).%20%E2%80%9CSuddenly%2C%20families%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20spend%20lakhs%20on%20a%20new%20solar%20system.%20With%20a%20modest%20investment%20in%20iCON%20and%20panels%2C%20they%20could%20turn%20their%20old%20inverters%20into%20solar%20inverters%20overnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harsh%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fsolar-inverter-4-1756908948.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20Left%3A%20Harsh%20Mohan%2C%20Dr%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Gopal%2C%20Nishanth%20CP%2C%20Lakshmi%20Nambiar%2C%20Kiran%20S.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%